Leaf-1, Tenant-B: 2001:db8:0:1::200 (End.DT46)&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;div class="hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0">
