&lt;div class="hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4">&lt;/div>
&lt;/button>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;p>Border leaf анонсирует EVPN routes в core. End-to-end SRv6, никаких gateway.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Вариант 2 - DC на VXLAN, core на SRv6:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code">
&lt;div>&lt;pre>&lt;code>VXLAN Fabric &amp;lt;-&amp;gt; BorderPE &amp;lt;-&amp;gt; SRv6 Core&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;div class="hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0">
